{"parse":{"title":"High Grade Build Fighters","pageid":56984,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><figure class=\"mw-default-size mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/9/92/HGBFLogo.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20160815094530\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"HGBFLogo\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"200\" height=\"140\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"HGBFLogo.jpg\" data-image-key=\"HGBFLogo.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/9/92/HGBFLogo.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20160815094530\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n<p><b>High Grade Build Fighters (HGBF)</b><span style=\"font-weight: normal\"> (<span class=\"t_nihongo_kanji\" lang=\"ja\">\u30cf\u30a4\u30b0\u30ec\u30fc\u30c9\u30d3\u30eb\u30c9\u30d5\u30a1\u30a4\u30bf\u30fc\u30ba</span><span class=\"t_nihongo_comma\" style=\"display:none\">,</span> <i><span class=\"t_nihongo_romaji\">Hai Gur\u0113do Birudo Fait\u0101zu</span></i><span class=\"t_nihongo_help\"><sup><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:Japanese\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Help:Japanese\"><span class=\"t_nihongo_icon\" style=\"color:#00e;font:bold 80% sans-serif;text-decoration:none;padding:0 .1em;\">?</span></a></sup></span>)</span> is a line of <a href=\"/wiki/Gunpla\" title=\"Gunpla\">Gunpla</a> kits of the <a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Weapon\" title=\"Mobile Weapon\">Mobile Suits</a> from <a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Fighters\" title=\"Gundam Build Fighters\">Gundam Build Fighters</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Fighters_Try\" title=\"Gundam Build Fighters Try\">Gundam Build Fighters Try</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Fighters_Try_Island_Wars\" title=\"Gundam Build Fighters Try Island Wars\">Gundam Build Fighters Try Island Wars</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Fighters:_GM%27s_Counterattack\" title=\"Gundam Build Fighters: GM&#39;s Counterattack\">Gundam Build Fighters: GM's Counterattack</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Fighters:_Battlogue\" title=\"Gundam Build Fighters: Battlogue\">Gundam Build Fighters: Battlogue</a> series in the <i>Gundam</i> meta series. It is split into two lines: the standard HG 1/144 model kits and <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Build_Custom\" title=\"High Grade Build Custom\">High Grade Build Custom</a>, which consists of accessories to enhance other Gunpla kits.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\"><span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#91;</span>1<span class=\"cite-bracket\">&#93;</span></a></sup> The HGBF line also includes the sub-lines <b>SD Build Fighters (SDBF)</b> and <b>Figure-rise Standard BUILD FIGHTERS TRY (FRSBFT)</b>.\n</p><p>Following the reorganization of Bandai Namco Group, box covers of reissue and future release of kits from September 2018 onwards feature a blue Bandai logo instead of the original red logo, while releases and reissues from mid-2022 onwards feature the Bandai Namco logo on the upper right corner (rarely, on the upper left corner below the HGBF logo).\n</p>\n<div style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Regulars_and_Special_Editions\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Regulars and Special Editions</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Exclusives\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Exclusives</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Trivia\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Trivia</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Regulars_and_Special_Editions\">Regulars and Special Editions</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgundam.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FHigh_Grade_Build_Fighters%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"tabber wds-tabber\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__wrapper with-bottom-border\"><ul class=\"wds-tabs\"><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab wds-is-current\" data-hash=\"Gundam_Build_Fighters_\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Gundam Build Fighters </a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Gundam_Build_Fighters_Try_\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Gundam Build Fighters Try </a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Gundam_Build_Fighters_Try_Island_Wars_\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Gundam Build Fighters Try Island Wars </a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Gundam_Build_Fighters:_GM&#39;s_Counterattack\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Gundam Build Fighters: GM's Counterattack</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Gundam_Build_Fighters:_Battlogue_\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Gundam Build Fighters: Battlogue </a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Side_Stories_\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Side Stories </a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Special_Editions_\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Special Editions </a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Other_\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Other </a></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content wds-is-current\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p><table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>HGBF #\n</th>\n<th>Model\n</th>\n<th>Series\n</th>\n<th>Yen Price\n</th>\n<th>Release Date\n</th>\n<th>Notes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>001 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/6/65/Hgbf_01.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20131112224831\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"Hgbf 01\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/6/65/Hgbf_01.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20131112224831\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"82\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Hgbf 01.jpg\" data-image-key=\"Hgbf_01.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GAT-X105B/FP_Build_Strike_Gundam_Full_Package\" title=\"GAT-X105B/FP Build Strike Gundam Full Package\">GAT-X105B/FP Build Strike Gundam Full Package</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Fighters\" title=\"Gundam Build Fighters\">Gundam Build Fighters</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,400\n</td>\n<td>2013 October\n</td>\n<td>First kit in the line. Includes Build Booster, which is also sold separately as <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Build_Custom\" title=\"High Grade Build Custom\">HGBC-001</a>. Mold of the kit is later used to create <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Universal_Century\" title=\"High Grade Universal Century\">HGCE</a>-171.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>002 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/4/43/Hgbf_02.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20131112224857\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"Hgbf 02\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/4/43/Hgbf_02.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20131112224857\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"82\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Hgbf 02.jpg\" data-image-key=\"Hgbf_02.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/MS-06R-AB_Zaku_Amazing\" title=\"MS-06R-AB Zaku Amazing\">MS-06R-AB Zaku Amazing</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Fighters\" title=\"Gundam Build Fighters\">Gundam Build Fighters</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,800\n</td>\n<td>2013 October\n</td>\n<td>Parts and color variant of <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Universal_Century\" title=\"High Grade Universal Century\">HGUC</a>-151. Includes weapons and armor parts that are also sold separately as HGBC-002.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>003 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/7/78/Hgbf_03.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20131107181340\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"Hgbf 03\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/7/78/Hgbf_03.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20131107181340\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"82\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Hgbf 03.jpg\" data-image-key=\"Hgbf_03.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/GX-9999_Gundam_X_Maoh\" title=\"GX-9999 Gundam X Maoh\">GX-9999 Gundam X Maoh</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Fighters\" title=\"Gundam Build Fighters\">Gundam Build Fighters</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,800\n</td>\n<td>2013 November\n</td>\n<td>Parts and color variant of HGAW-109.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>004 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/e/e2/Hgbf_04.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20131124222047\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"Hgbf 04\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"83\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"Hgbf 04.jpg\" data-image-key=\"Hgbf_04.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/e/e2/Hgbf_04.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20131124222047\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/RX-178B_Build_Gundam_Mk-II\" title=\"RX-178B Build Gundam Mk-II\">RX-178B Build Gundam Mk-II</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Fighters\" title=\"Gundam Build Fighters\">Gundam Build Fighters</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,800\n</td>\n<td>2013 November\n</td>\n<td>Color variant of HGUC-030 with new V-fin, left trigger finger hand, and chest and beam effect parts. Includes Build Booster Mk-II, which is also sold separately as HGBC-003.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>005 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/c/cb/Beargguy_III_Box.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20250307042641\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"Beargguy III Box\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"80\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"Beargguy III Box.jpg\" data-image-key=\"Beargguy_III_Box.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/c/cb/Beargguy_III_Box.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20250307042641\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/KUMA-03_Beargguy_III\" title=\"KUMA-03 Beargguy III\">KUMA-03 Beargguy III (SAN)</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Fighters\" title=\"Gundam Build Fighters\">Gundam Build Fighters</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,800\n</td>\n<td>2013 December\n</td>\n<td>Parts and color variant of <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Gunpla_Builders\" title=\"High Grade Gunpla Builders\">HGGB</a>-04. Includes adapter for different types of 1/144 backpacks or to fit Ribbon Striker on other kits.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>006 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/5/54/HG_Wing_Gundam_Fenice.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20131125154001\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"HG Wing Gundam Fenice\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"82\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"HG Wing Gundam Fenice.jpg\" data-image-key=\"HG_Wing_Gundam_Fenice.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/5/54/HG_Wing_Gundam_Fenice.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20131125154001\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/XXXG-01Wf_Wing_Gundam_Fenice\" title=\"XXXG-01Wf Wing Gundam Fenice\">XXXG-01Wf Wing Gundam Fenice</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Fighters\" title=\"Gundam Build Fighters\">Gundam Build Fighters</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,600\n</td>\n<td>2013 December\n</td>\n<td>Parts and color variant of HGAC-162. Meteor Hopper is sold separately as HGBC-004.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>007 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/9/9e/HG_Sengoku_Astray_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20131125154226\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"HG Sengoku Astray Gundam\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"82\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"HG Sengoku Astray Gundam.jpg\" data-image-key=\"HG_Sengoku_Astray_Gundam.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/9/9e/HG_Sengoku_Astray_Gundam.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20131125154226\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/%E4%BE%8D%E3%83%8E%E5%BC%90_Sengoku_Astray_Gundam\" title=\"\u4f8d\u30ce\u5f10 Sengoku Astray Gundam\">\u4f8d\u30ce\u5f10 Sengoku Astray Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Gundam_Build_Fighters\" title=\"Gundam Build Fighters\">Gundam Build Fighters</a>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,800\n</td>\n<td>2013 December\n</td>\n<td>Parts variant of <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Gundam_SEED\" title=\"High Grade Gundam SEED\">HG SEED</a>-58.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>008 <figure class=\"mw-halign-right\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/b/b0/HG_Kampfer_Amazing.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20131226112452\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"HG Kampfer Amazing\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"130\" height=\"82\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"HG Kampfer Amazing.jpg\" data-image-key=\"HG_Kampfer_Amazing.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/b/b0/HG_Kampfer_Amazing.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/130?cb=20131226112452\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/PPMS-18E_K%C3%A4mpfer_Amazing\" title=\"PPMS-18E K\u00e4mpfer Amazing\">PPMS-18E K\u00e4mpfer Ama